config LED_IS31FL3235A
	bool "IS31FL3235A LED driver"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_ISSI_IS31FL3235A_ENABLED
	select I2C
	help
	  Enable driver for IS31FL3235A LED controller.

	  The IS31FL3235A is a 28-channel constant current LED driver
	  from Lumissil Microsystems (ISSI) with I2C interface.

	  Features:
	  - 28 independent LED channels
	  - 8-bit PWM brightness control per channel
	  - Per-channel current scaling (1x, 1/2x, 1/3x, 1/4x)
	  - Selectable PWM frequency (3kHz or 22kHz)
	  - Hardware and software shutdown modes
	  - Up to 38mA per channel (set by external resistor)
